    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将玻璃送到客户手中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为两名建筑工人，你们要为一座摩天大楼运送玻璃窗。在运输过程中，你们必须小心翼翼，因为玻璃非常易碎。你们能顺利到达摩天大楼的顶部而不打碎玻璃吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏： 找朋友帮忙搬运玻璃！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请一位值得信赖的朋友到大厅和你一起搬运玻璃！      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=644 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >带物理功能的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们为角色的每个部分都添加了物理效果，以提高游戏的可玩性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=592 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式： 简单、困难（无检查点）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你想要更休闲的体验，不妨试试简单模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但如果你相信自己能在不打破玻璃的情况下到达顶端，那么困难模式可能会适合你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras_big/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318 width=800 height=274 /></span></p>",
